{"tid":2251940,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"點解Share Tea會突然重新冒起仲做左龍頭","createTime":"2020-10-21T06:55:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T18:22:42.000Z","uid":252078,"like":4,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"faacaaed68138e374dbdae0966f6247d6bae1dc4","tid":2251940,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"我記得Share Tea啱啱開果果時紅過一排<br />\n但競爭太激烈<br />\n於是好快就做唔住 汁左好多分店<br />\n<br />\n之後又過左幾年<br />\n突然發現各區都多左好多ShareTea分店<br />\n係而家香港台式奶茶界黎講佢應該都算係龍頭<br />\n分店最多應該係佢(?) <br />\n利申無stat 純粹憑感覺<br />\n反而當年既龍頭貢茶就無左影<br />\n<br />\n老實講Share Tea唔係特別好飲<br />\n各方面都只係中規中矩<br />\n茶味唔夠天仁濃<br />\n珍珠唔夠老虎堂正<br />\n係勝在款式多 分店多 夠就腳<br />\n其實佢係憑乜開到咁多分店 <br />\n仲要撐到而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n定得我一個覺得佢d野飲一般<br />\n其他人大部分覺得好正？"},{"pid":"ebd1a444e285261d49903c59555cf8ca7e7f468b","tid":2251940,"uid":227419,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"Share Tea 幾時變咗龍頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7044b1dff81eda329b96ca52466bbe81a84685b7","tid":2251940,"uid":99397,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:57:09.000Z","msg":"拉，<br />\nPR post"},{"pid":"022a297cefcb0ed28cfcb9b2a9714f0869e994aa","tid":2251940,"uid":252078,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"ebd1a444e285261d49903c59555cf8ca7e7f468b","tid":2251940,"uid":227419,"like":71,"dislike":0,"score":71,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:56:27.000Z","msg":"Share Tea 幾時變咗龍頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T06:57:50.000Z","msg":"佢分店真係超多<br />\n好似無另一間台式奶茶d分店多到好似佢咁<br />\n佢真係做到梗有一個係你左梗"},{"pid":"0b36a5e9791793b0cb1413886e349e840ad80133","tid":2251940,"uid":38904,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"